# Google AI Studio API key for full Ragas evaluation with Gemini
# Get yours at: https://aistudio.google.com → "Get API Key" → "Create API key"
# When set, `python -m app.evaluation.evaluate` uses Gemini as the LLM judge
# When unset, evaluation falls back to free local heuristics
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_ai_studio_key_here
